{"tid":779150,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［高達］The-o vs Zeta gundam???","createTime":"2018-08-14T08:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T13:25:17.000Z","uid":28042,"like":21,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"a08170232369c50e74e7663f3cfcd047c15a305e","tid":779150,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"隔離po 見到好多人誤會The-o 比Zeta 高級<br />\n又有人講埋泰坦斯新型機強過Zeta<br />\n<br />\n呢個誤解都幾深下，Zeta 呢部癲野係0087年最top, 沒有之一<br />\n<br />\n簡單比較下兩部性能<br />\n<br />\nZeta:<br />\n裝甲：高達尼姆合金&gamma;<br />\n出力：2020KW<br />\n推進力：5&times;12200KG+2&times;10600KG+4&times;7600KG=112600KG <br />\n加速力：1.81G<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe-O<br />\n裝甲：高達尼姆合金<br />\n出力：1840KW<br />\n推進力：1&times;38200KG+6&times;16200KG=135400KG<br />\n加速度： 1.57G<br />\n<br />\n睇落The-o 唯一強過Zeta 嘅係推進力<br />\n但Zeta 重量輕20噸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n武裝方面，<br />\nThe-o 得beam，rifle 同saber<br />\nZeta 有埋實彈<br />\n<br />\nZeta 仲要多個bio-sensor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於姿勢制御噴嘴The-o有50個<br />\n多過Zeta 42個，原因係木星圈宙域多碎石，<br />\n引力高，所以姿勢制御要求高啲<br />\n<br />\n比盡你呢樣勁過Zeta, The-O 點都係下位過Zeta 好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家要記得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938292d794c344d4788e722a3e6cfad96b14d64d","tid":779150,"uid":28042,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"推俾以為The-o 好撚勁嘅傻豬睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9885242ca4008d569d397b412158d93b08e01d9","tid":779150,"uid":61082,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"鐵奧，點解唔郁呀，鐵奧！"},{"pid":"d85f12ba65615780be71523c41ed61d6c3589127","tid":779150,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"有兩個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪隔離po 吹奏The-O 嘅傻豬俾我？<br />\n係咪好嬲，但係見到咁多資料冇聲出呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2cbf88875c7ab95ec065eb981e5d49a908fa2c","tid":779150,"uid":8307,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"淨係個bio-sensor已經屈左G la"},{"pid":"16de33a4210de56d7ce9bb3c9fc3a2607ec7b252","tid":779150,"uid":34858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea2cbf88875c7ab95ec065eb981e5d49a908fa2c","tid":779150,"uid":8307,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"淨係個bio-sensor已經屈左G la"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"我Agger"},{"pid":"28366143a81dd2f0e51ab6a6007b4a0247327386","tid":779150,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16de33a4210de56d7ce9bb3c9fc3a2607ec7b252","tid":779150,"uid":34858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea2cbf88875c7ab95ec065eb981e5d49a908fa2c","tid":779150,"uid":8307,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"淨係個bio-sensor已經屈左G la"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"我Agger"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:02:42.000Z","msg":"根本兩個層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d78adc368869d6aa1d17d3d4b39e63eb26dd50d","tid":779150,"uid":73473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"但係the-O埋身有鹹豬手喎<br />\n利申，無立場"},{"pid":"6b6f65c11feb57a6a7cecdab20bc060435614fc7","tid":779150,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:19:22.000Z","msg":"你解釋吓The-O定身之迷先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebc392ab9f5110aaf0c4662d8bd0c2802c79ce4","tid":779150,"uid":28042,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quo